```{=html}
<ul class="list">
<% for (const item of items) { %>
  <li class="project" <%= metadataAttrs(item) %>>
    <div class="project-content">
    <p><% if (item['pub_status']) { %><span class="status btn-<% item['pub_status'].class %>"><i class="fas <% item['pub_status'].icon %>"></i> <% item['pub_status'].status %></span> <% } %><% item['citation'] %></p>
            </div>
    <a href="<%- item.href %>" class="listing-name"><%= item.name %></a><br/>
    <span class="listing-custom-field"><%= item['custom-field'] %><span>
  </li>
<% } %>
</ul>
```
